<div style=\"text-align: left;\">
</div>
<div style=\"text-align: left;\">
<br />
Finally, we will be soon making some updates to the Developer Distribution Agreement (DDA), which includes the ability for family members to share purchased apps on Google Play. Here you can see the <a href=\"https://play.google.com/about/developer-distribution-agreement/upcoming.html\" target=\"_blank\">updated DDA</a>.<br />
<br /></div>
