To learn more about all of these features, tune-in live to ‘<a href=\"https://events.google.com/io2016/schedule?filters=Play&amp;sid=fc003c22-230b-e611-a517-00155d5066d7#day2/fc003c22-230b-e611-a517-00155d5066d7\" target=\"_blank\">What’s new in Google Play for developers</a>’ at 11am PDT / 2pm EDT / 7:00pm GMT+1 on May 19 on the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/GoogleDevelopers\" target=\"_blank\">Google Developers YouTube channel</a>.<br />
