apps can now:
</p><ul>
<li>Organize photos that contain text
<li>Automate tedious data entry for credit cards, receipts, and business cards
<li>Translate documents (along with the <a
href=\"https://cloud.google.com/translate/\">Cloud Translate API</a>)
