changes</a>. For details on how to setup your app with the final SDK, see <a
href=\"https://developer.android.com/preview/setup-sdk.html?utm_campaign=android_launch_npreview_061516&utm_source=anddev&utm_medium=blog\">Set up the
Preview</a>. For details on API level 24 check out the <a
